data.description: Absolutely stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bath home with a modern and open floor plan that creates a seamless flow throughout. The main living areas feature easy care tile flooring, and the kitchen is a chef's dream with granite countertops, a gourmet island, gas cooktop, and a convenient pantry. The luxurious master suite is a retreat in itself, boasting a double sink vanity and a generously sized walk-in closet. You'll appreciate the comfort of refrigerated central air throughout the home, ensuring a pleasant environment year-round. This home is not just beautifully designed but also convenient, situated in a prime location. The newer roof, installed in 2022, provides peace of mind. Step outside to a delightful patio and a walled backyard, creating a private oasis for relaxation and entertainment. Don't miss the chance to make this meticulously maintained and thoughtfully upgraded property your new home!
